title: Fraggle Rock Season 4 - XviD DVDRip
description:
XviD DVD Rips of the fourth season of the 80's HBO series, Fraggle Rock.

After releasing a season a year on DVD starting in 2005, when it came time to release this final season this year, they decided to only make it available as part of a box set with the first three seasons, screwing over fans that already bought the first three.

The ratings at Amazon.com for the box set are horrible. If you guys care, write some angry reviews there, and/or contact the company releasing them directly to complain.

If you are one of the people boycotting purchasing any more of this series (at least until the fourth season comes out individually), enjoy this release.


Note:
The first upload had the audio messed up in most of the files.  It has been fixed in this release.
